(C.55)"
REFERENCES,0.6346863468634686,"where Q is an orthogonal matrix, U (ℓ) is a column-orthogonal matrix, and V (z; U) is deﬁned
in Equation (C.54). Consequently, the paraunitary system H(z) is parameterized by L + L + 1
(column-)orthogonal matrices Q and U (ℓ)’s."
REFERENCES,0.6359163591635917,Under review as a conference paper at ICLR 2022
